Class ParametersMap

All Implemented Interfaces:
Map, Serializable
public final class ParametersMap
extends Parameters
implements Map

Wrapper class for Parameters class that exposes parameters through Map interface.

Use this wrapper if you want to put Parameters in ObjectModel.
